    <head>Appendix: Glossary</head>
    
    <list type="gloss">
        <label>Morpheus</label>
        <item>The Morpheus morphological analysis service is a tool originally developed by Perseus,
            versions of which are in use by Papyri.info and the TLG for lemmatizing their Greek texts.
            The Perseus version of the tool also caters for Latin and Arabic lemmatization.
            [<ref target="https://wiki.projectbamboo.org/display/BDOC/Morphological+Analysis+Service"
                >Reference page for Morphological Analysis Service</ref>]
        </item>
    </list>
    
    
